headline: Los Olivos Gritan 'malditos' a asesinos de estudiante
subheadline: En la colonia del Departamento donde murió, en Los Olivos
author: Cirllo
content: Residents in Los Olivos shouted insults at the killers of a student. Miguel Sánchez Castaño allegedly killed his cousin Martín Castaño on February 19th. The suspects used mototaxis for their crimes and were involved in a robbery. Police are providing security to those at risk from the criminals.
